6d/f1/3948_Dl7An.jpg"},"summary":"　　这是一场被加尔德罗贝封印的战争。讲述风华王家之秘，和爱莉卡的母亲＝雷娜·塞亚斯的故事。\r\n　　憧憬着乙HiME的少女＝西弗尔。某一天，魔手袭击了在无依无靠的同时仍坚强生存着的她。谜之组织「希巴鲁兹」们拐走了西弗尔。在危急时刻，将她救出的是黑衣绅士＝布鲁斯，他的女仆(?)＝蕾娜，紫苑修女和她的乙HiME＝Meister拉凯尔，以及五柱·一之柱=艾利奥特。\r\n　　少女西弗尔之谜。\r\n　　拥有乙HiME力量却将其拒绝的蕾娜。\r\n　　加尔德罗贝之谜。\r\n　　五柱的背叛。\r\n　　现在，正是先代乙HiME觉醒之时。\r\n　　标题中的“S.ifr”包含了两层意思：其一，它在阿拉伯语中是0的意思；其二，它也提示了作品中的主要角色西弗尔・布兰（Sifr Flan）。","name":"舞-乙HiME 0 ～S.ifr～","name_cn":"舞-乙HiME 0～S.ifr～","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":94,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":82,"total_cont":0},{"name":"舞-乙HiME","count":73,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":72,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2008","count":50,"total_cont":0},{"name":"前传","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"太太我喜欢你呀","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"久行宏和","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"娘战士","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"苍天の青玉","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日升","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"变身","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Zhime","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"少女高达","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"舞-HiME","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"梶浦由记","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2008年2月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"樋口達人","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"沢上水也","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"07","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"舞-乙HiME 0～S.ifr～"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"cn","v":"舞-乙HiME OVA第2弹"},{"k":"en","v":"Mai-Otome Sifr"},{"k":"jp","v":"マイオトメ シフル"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"3"},{"key":"发售日","value":"2008年2月22日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.my-zhime.net/sifr/index.html"},{"key":"开始","value":"2008年2月22日"}